Package: StatsSample
Type: Package
Title: Easily Calculate Accurate Sample Sizes
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Pedro Henrique Theotonio de Mesquita Pacheco
Maintainer: Pedro Henrique Theotonio de Mesquita Pacheco <pedrohmp36@gmail.com>
Description: StatsSample is an R package designed to simplify the quick and accurate
   calculation of sample sizes in clinical trials and other statistical research.
   It streamlines this process, providing detailed calculations that ensure the
   robustness and validity of results without the need for external tools or
   complex manual computations.
